<br>
The coolest part is level 1 to, say, 30 will be generic and easy and the game will get harder the higher you level. You have like 4 or 5 classes at level 1 (depending on whether you count the trader as a class) and a lot more at level 100 (they are saying there will be 48 classes but that's counting ALL the archtypes and subclasses e.g. fighter-&gt;brawler-&gt;paladin), so roles become more specialised as you level up.<br>
<br>
